<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفْلَحَ}</span> ... فَازَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اللَّغْوِ}</span> ... مَا لَا خَيْرَ فِيهِ مِنَ الأَقْوَالِ وَالأَفْعَالِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أوْ مَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَانُهُمْ}</span> ... الإِمَاءِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْعَادُونَ}</span> ... المُجَاوِزُونَ الحَلَالَ إِلَى الحَرَامِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَاعُونَ}</span> ... حَافِظُونَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْفِرْدَوْسَ}</span> ... أَعْلَى مَنَازِلِ الجَنَّةِ، وَهُوَ أَعْلَى مَنَازِلِ الجَنَّةِ وَأَوْسَطُهَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُلَالَةٍ مِّن طِينٍ}</span> ... مَاخُوذٍ ومُسْتَلٍّ مِنْ جَمِيعِ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُطْفَةً}</span> ... مَنِيَّ الرِّجَالِ يَخْرُجُ مِنْ أَصْلَابِهِمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَرَارٍ مَّكِينٍ}</span> ... هُوَ الرَّحِمُ تَسْتَقِرُّ فِيهِ النُّطْفَةُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَقَةً}</span> ... دَمًا أَحْمَرَ مُلْتَصِقًا بِالرَّحِمِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُضْغَةً}</span> ... قِطْعَةَ لَحْمٍ قَدْرَ مَا يُمْضَغُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَرَائِقَ}</span> ... سَمَوَاتٍ بَعْضُهَا فَوْقَ بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِقَدَرٍ}</span> ... بِمِقْدَارِ حَاجَةِ الخَلْقِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَجَرَةً}</span> ... هِيَ شَجَرَةُ الزَّيْتُونِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالدُّهْنِ}</span> ... بِالزَّيْتِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
